com.invensense.casdk.client

Class BluetoothDataReader

  • java.lang.Object
      • com.invensense.casdk.client.BluetoothDataReader

  • public final class BluetoothDataReader
extends
    This class is responsible for handling communication between the wearable sensor and the Android application. Data is read here and stored in a Global variable for other classes to access.
